Recommends:
 nm-connection-editor,
 gnome-keyring | kwalletmanager,
Description: NetworkManager VPN plugin for openfortivpn
 This package provides NetworkManager integration for openfortivpn,
 an open-source client for Fortinet SSL VPN (FortiGate).
 .
 Features:
  - Connect/disconnect via nmcli, nmtui, or GUI
  - Secure password storage via GNOME Keyring or KWallet
  - Untrusted certificate detection and trust workflow
  - Full settings editor in nm-connection-editor
  - DNS and routing configuration
